StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [sp_GetO.cerMissingDocuments]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@ContractID integer AS
SELECT [MISSING_DOC_ID], [CONTRACT_ID], [DATE_ENTERED], [COMMENTS], [LEVEL], [ASSIGNED], [DUE_DATE], [STATUS], [USER_LOGIN], [UPDATE_DATE] FROM [MISSING_DOCUMENTS] WHERE [CONTRACT_ID] = @ContractID ORDER BY [DUE_DATE] asc, [MISSING_DOC_ID] asc
